"{\"uid\": \"myrepublica.nagariknetwork.com-news-komorebi-is-the-official-clothing-partner-of-nepali-team-for-paris-olympics\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Subscribe Now  NOC signs four-year partnership deal with French apparel brand Komorebi  KATHMANDU, March 4: Nepal Olympic Committee (NOC) has signed an agreement with French apparel brand Komorebi as the official clothing partner of Nepal for the 33rd Summer Olympics in Paris, France.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 285, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 15, \"end\": 18, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 0.9999991077460778, \"rank\": 8.922141013368361e-07, \"text\": \"NOC\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Olympic_Committee\"}, {\"begin\": 57, \"end\": 63, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9922361439241394, \"rank\": 0.005370866041185205, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}, {\"begin\": 108, \"end\": 131, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nepal_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Nepal Olympic Committee\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nepal_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nepal_Olympic_Committee\"}, {\"begin\": 133, \"end\": 136, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 0.9999991077460778, \"rank\": 8.922141013368361e-07, \"text\": \"NOC\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Olympic_Committee\"}, {\"begin\": 167, \"end\": 173, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9922361439241394, \"rank\": 0.005370866041185205, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}, {\"begin\": 233, \"end\": 238, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nepal\", \"score\": 0.9999999999988631, \"rank\": 1.2353350407181506e-12, \"text\": \"Nepal\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nepal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nepal\"}, {\"begin\": 271, \"end\": 276, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999985144717932, \"rank\": 1.4855304176357714e-06, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 278, \"end\": 284, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.6339667098746793, \"rank\": 0.5717483939531449, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"NOC Secretary General Nilendraraj Shrestha and Daniel Valetin, CEO for Komorebi, signed the agreement on behalf of their respective organizations on Sunday.\", \"from\": 286, \"to\": 442, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 286, \"end\": 289, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 0.9999991077460778, \"rank\": 8.922141013368361e-07, \"text\": \"NOC\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Olympic_Committee\"}, {\"begin\": 320, \"end\": 328, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shresthas\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Shrestha\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shresthas\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shresthas\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As per the agreement, Komorebi will provide sports dress to the members of the Nepalese team who will participate in the Paris Olympics.\", \"from\": 444, \"to\": 580, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 523, \"end\": 531, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nepal\", \"score\": 0.999999991046252, \"rank\": 3.8903068182979645e-09, \"text\": \"Nepalese\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nepal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nepal\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The term of the agreement will expire after four years.\", \"from\": 582, \"to\": 637, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"According to the agreement, Komorebi will also provide uniforms to the Nepali team for competitions held under the International Olympic Committee and Olympic Council of Asia.\", \"from\": 638, \"to\": 813, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 709, \"end\": 715, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nepal\", \"score\": 0.9999994530375392, \"rank\": 5.365804346339845e-07, \"text\": \"Nepali\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nepal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nepal\"}, {\"begin\": 753, \"end\": 784, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"International Olympic Committee\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"These include Summer and Winter Olympics, Summer and Winter Asian Games, Summer and Winter Youth Olympics, Asian Beach Games and South Asian Games.\", \"from\": 814, \"to\": 961, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 921, \"end\": 938, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Asian_Beach_Games\", \"score\": 0.9999989520511952, \"rank\": 1.0477016887989502e-06, \"text\": \"Asian Beach Games\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Asian_Beach_Games\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Asian_Beach_Games\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"At the request of the NOC, logos of other institutes can also be placed on the uniforms provided by Komorebi.\", \"from\": 963, \"to\": 1072, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 985, \"end\": 988, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 0.9999991077460778, \"rank\": 8.922141013368361e-07, \"text\": \"NOC\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Olympic_Committee\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"NOC President Jeevan Ram Shrestha and Nepal Judo Association President Deepak Harsha Bajracharya were also present at the signing ceremony held at the NOC headquarters in Satdobato.\", \"from\": 1074, \"to\": 1255, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1074, \"end\": 1077, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 0.9999991077460778, \"rank\": 8.922141013368361e-07, \"text\": \"NOC\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Olympic_Committee\"}, {\"begin\": 1088, \"end\": 1107, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jeevan_Ram_Shrestha\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Jeevan Ram Shrestha\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jeevan_Ram_Shrestha\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jeevan_Ram_Shrestha\"}, {\"begin\": 1112, \"end\": 1117, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nepal\", \"score\": 0.9999999999988631, \"rank\": 1.2353350407181506e-12, \"text\": \"Nepal\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nepal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nepal\"}, {\"begin\": 1118, \"end\": 1122, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Judo\", \"score\": 0.9999992000526634, \"rank\": 5.976776477805093e-07, \"text\": \"Judo\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Judo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/